This involves the use of algorithms and mathematical equations to calculate the grades, which suggests that the paper could belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses formal properties of the PeerRank method, which could fall under the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) or Cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-categories.
